# ‡πÇ‡∏õ‡∏£‡πÅ‡∏Å‡∏£‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏´‡∏±‡∏™‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏ñ‡∏≠‡∏î‡∏£‡∏´‡∏±‡∏™‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö Transposition Cipher
def transposition_encrypt(text):
    result = ""
    for i in range(0, len(text), 2):
        # ‡∏™‡∏•‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏ï‡∏≥‡πÅ‡∏´‡∏ô‡πà‡∏á‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏Å‡∏©‡∏£‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô‡∏Ñ‡∏π‡πà (‡πÄ‡∏ä‡πà‡∏ô AB -> BA)
        if i + 1 < len(text):
            result += text[i + 1] + text[i]
        else:
            result += text[i]  # ‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏™‡∏∏‡∏î‡∏ó‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏´‡∏≤‡∏Å‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô‡∏Ñ‡∏µ‡πà‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏™‡∏•‡∏±‡∏ö
    return result

def transposition_decrypt(text):
    return transposition_encrypt(text)  # ‡∏™‡∏•‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏Å‡∏•‡∏±‡∏ö‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏ü‡∏±‡∏á‡∏Å‡πå‡∏ä‡∏±‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏¥‡∏°

try:
    plaintext = input("Enter plaintext (Alphabet Only): ")

    # ‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏´‡∏±‡∏™‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö Transposition
    ciphertext = transposition_encrypt(plaintext)
